     <div type="encomium">
   <pb facs="3"/>
   <head>To my friend M<seg rend="sup">r</seg>. IOHN FORD.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>VNto this Altar, rich with thy owne spice,</l>
      <l>I bring one graine, to thy <hi>Loves Sacrifice:</hi>
      </l>
      <l>And boast to see thy flames ascending, while</l>
      <l>Perfumes enrich our Ayre from thy sweet Pile.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>Looke here <hi>THOV</hi> that hast <hi>malice</hi> to the Stage,</l>
      <l>And <hi>Impudence</hi> enough for the whole Age;</l>
      <l>
         <hi>Voluminously-Ignorant!</hi> be vext</l>
      <l>To read this Tragedy, and thy owne be next.</l>
   </lg>
   <p>James Shirley.</p>
</div>
